    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This high-revving engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, remains exceptionally responsive. Crucial enthusiast-grade maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise shift action, sending power through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its signature balance with refreshed bushings and a well-damped suspension setup. While the car exhibits honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain and structural integrity are prioritized, making it an ideal candidate for a purist driver seeking a communicative and visceral performance machine.",
